comment:
Thank you all for 2k oml I was NOT expecting it to get this much traction

Everyone who’s said anything nice about this video; I WILL die for you. You cannot change this.
OwO I love how you’ve drawn aziraphale, it’s so lovely 10/10  approve
This is too cute!! The way you matched the lyrics is perfect.  I love the "innocence dies screaming" and "like my mirror long ago" parts

Your art style is absolutely adorable! I loved how expressive you made them, you did such an amazing job of capturing aziraphale's embarrassment in the scene with Adam and the thoughtless kindness with Crowley. Ntm crowley's looks of just absolute awe and adoration were amazing!!! Your animatic was gorgeous, i am def subscribing and look forward to seeing any of your future works!
I absolutely love this,! The expressions, artstyle & symbolism is on point!
